name: Futzi
review: Don't do these blades to your saws! Irregularly set teeth and super thick paint, swing sideways when sawing.The worst hands I've had so far!

name: Stern
review: I'm surprised that these saw blades cut better and lasted longer than the saw blades from a well-known manufacturer that I would have used before.

name: Eddy
review: Purchased the 9 inch Jigsaw to cut branches on trees with my Reciprocating saw. Worked well and did not snap. Very satisfied with my purchase.
